<h1 id="table">Table</h1>
<p>Presents tabular data with multiple rows and columns. The table&#39;s width is flexible, but it does not have any advanced responsive behaviors.</p>
<h2 id="variants">Variants</h2>
<h3 id="default">Default</h3>
<p>The column widths are determined by the content. {{> Table props=TableExampleModel}}
</p>
<h3 id="fixed">Fixed</h3>
<p>The columns are split evenly, regardless of their content. {{> Table props=TableFixedExampleModel}}
</p>
<h3 id="selectable">Selectable</h3>
<p>Rows can be selected. {{> Table props=TableSelectableExampleModel}}
</p>
